messages.subject: Post-Workout Recovery Tips
messages.msgText: Don't forget to hydrate and consume a protein-rich meal after your workouts!

messages.subject: New Bootcamp Class
messages.msgText: Join us for a new bootcamp class starting next week. It'll be fun and challenging!

messages.subject: Yoga Classes Cancelled
messages.msgText: Sorry, but the yoga classes for this weekend are cancelled. We'll resume next week.

messages.subject: Healthy Eating Tips
messages.msgText: Remember to include a variety of fruits and vegetables in your diet for better health.

messages.subject: Cardio Challenge
messages.msgText: Who's up for a cardio challenge? Let's see who can burn the most calories this week.

messages.subject: Motivational Quote
messages.msgText: Keep going! Your hard work will pay off soon.

messages.subject: Gym Etiquette Reminder
messages.msgText: Please remember to wipe down your equipment after use. Let's keep our gym clean and safe.

messages.subject: Fitness Event
messages.msgText: There's a local marathon happening next month. Let's train and participate together!

messages.subject: Workout Playlist
messages.msgText: Just sharing my new workout playlist here. Hope it gets you pumped up!

messages.subject: Rest and Recovery
messages.msgText: Don't forget to give your body enough rest to recover and grow stronger. Goodnight everyone!
